<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▶&nbsp;附录1085-0069β：探索项目异常性质的音频日志记录</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;权限验证完成，附录已开启，点击返回主页</a></div>
